Click to watch George discuss whom PGIMC serves.
At Pacific Global Investment Management Company, we are value investors. We use patience and discipline as we seek to buy high quality, well-positioned companies at attractive prices. As focused investors, we know each company in which we invest, how it operates and what makes it successful. When we invest, we seek to invest for the long-term; we typically accumulate shares over time and pay reasonable prices. All along, we actively monitor each investment to respond to market opportunities.
We also invest in our clients. Our personal approach includes meetings with each client to understand objectives, interests and investment history. We listen to our clients and implement strategies based on their needs. As a result of our client-focused, tailored approach, no two client portfolios are identical.
We manage accounts for individuals, institutions and mutual funds including the Pacific Advisors Funds.


Investing in securities involves risk of loss that clients should be prepared to bear. Click here for a description of specific risks related to our investment strategies.




