Company Overview of Pacific Global Investment Management Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pacific Global Investment Management Company is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning, trust and estate planning, insurance and tax analysis, retirement planning, and education planning services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets across...
Pacific Global Investment Management Company is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning, trust and estate planning, insurance and tax analysis, retirement planning, and education planning services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm invests in the value stocks of large-cap, mid-cap, and small-cap companies for its equity investments. For its fixed income portfolios, it invests in the U.S. Government bonds, corporate bonds, and money market instruments. Pacific Global Investment Management Company is based in Glendale, California with additional offices in Maitland, Florida and Winter Garden, Florida.
Detailed Description


